What you need to know:  The church leadership says it preaches using the Bible, blending the Pokot traditions with ChristianityThe church with roots in West Pokot County is reaching out to those who have illegal guns to voluntarily surrender them to authoritiesIts leader- Aristi Kapel says they will be holding daily prayersFor the first time in the church’s history, 42 apostles graduated on Sunday at a ceremony attended by Switzerland’s ambassador to Kenya, Mr Valentin Zellweger